<appendix id="mig"><title>Migration</title>
<para>This appendix lists some differences between Open Object Rexx 5.0.0
and earlier versions of Open Object Rexx.</para>

<section id="deprecated"><title>Deprecated Rexx Utilities Semaphore functions</title>
<para>The following Rexx Utilities functions related to
semaphore-processing have been deprecated.
<simplelist columns="2">
 <member>SysCloseEventSem</member>
 <member>SysCloseMutexSem</member>
 <member>SysCreateEventSem</member>
 <member>SysCreateMutexSem</member>
 <member>SysOpenEventSem</member>
 <member>SysOpenMutexSem</member>
 <member>SysPostEventSem</member>
 <member>SysPulseEventSem</member>
 <member>SysReleaseMutexSem</member>
 <member>SysRequestMutexSem</member>
 <member>SysResetEventSem</member>
 <member>SysWaitEventSem</member>
</simplelist>
</para>
<para>The use any of these functions is strongly discouraged, no
documentation is provided and no bug reports against any of these
functions will be accepted.
They are expected to be removed in a future release of the interpreter.
</para>
<para>They have been superseded by the new
<xref linkend="ooRexxEventSemaphoreClass" xrefstyle="select:title"/> and
<xref linkend="ooRexxMutexSemaphoreClass" xrefstyle="select:title"/>.
</para>
</section>

